&             bitwise and
|             bitwise or
^             bitwise xor
~             bitwise not
<<            leftshift operator
>>            rightshift operator
------------------EVEN---------------------
LSB = 0
N & 1 = 0
------------------ODD---------------------
LSB = 1
N & 1 = 0



------------------MULTIPLY BY 2---------------------
LEFT SHIFT OPERATOR : << 
------------------DIVIDE BY 2---------------------
RIGHT SHIFT OPERATOR : >>



------------------OP POINTS---------------------
a^a^b^c^c^b^x = 0^x = x
------------------TO SET RIGHTMOST UNSET BIT---------------------
N | (N + 1)
------------------TO UNSET RIGHTMOST SET BIT(brian kernighan)---------------------
N & (N - 1)                                     